ing with this new Dokan add-on!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"enclosure\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"url\";s:67:\"http://docs.wedevs.com/assets/dokan-booking-customer-experience.mp4\";s:6:\"length\";s:6:\"734293\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"video/mp4\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Ranan Rahim\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10038:\"<p>This is great! The Dokan WC Bookings add-on opens up a whole new possibility for a variety of new products and vendors on your market. Also this means even markets based on booking products can now emerge.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-success\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/products/plugins/dokan/woocommerce-booking-integration/?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=can-now-book-products-events-hotels-anything-new-dokan-add\">All this just for $49!</a></p>\n<p>The add-on is designed specially for hotel booking, conference booking, concerts and all sorts of other services where you need your customers to book products. Any vendor can create bookable and regular or variable products side by side.</p>\n<p>The bookings have excellent customization capabilities. We are actually bringing all the features from the WooCommerce booking add-on to our frontend. The features on the backend of WooCommerce were harder to navigate and easier to get confused. But we have simplified a lot of things to suit vendors.</p>\n<h3>Create bookings with precise calendar accuracy</h3>\n<p>You can make your booking product available for several days only. You can also set days when the product will be published, but locked before the booking period actually starts. For example, you are a hotel manager and you have 3 luxury suits which you are posting online. But the holiday season starts in 3 days. So, you can easily post a booking product, with a three day no booking period and say, a one week booking time.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-002.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=can-now-book-products-events-hotels-anything-new-dokan-add&amp;x21811\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-80646\" src=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-002.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=can-now-book-products-events-hotels-anything-new-dokan-add&amp;x21811\" alt=\"new-booking-002\" width=\"930\" height=\"536\" srcset=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-002.png?x21811 930w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-002-300x173.png?x21811 300w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-002-768x443.png?x21811 768w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-002-600x346.png?x21811 600w?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=can-now-book-products-events-hotels-anything-new-dokan-add\" sizes=\"(max-width: 930px) 100vw, 930px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Sometimes, you can also sell your bookable products in volumes when you are targeting big. For example, you don&#8217;t want to book your room unless someone takes it for two days. That&#8217;s also possible.</p>\n<h3>Multiple booking in a day for serving multiple customers</h3>\n<p>So, let&#8217;s say you want to keep an option where your customer can rent your hotel room for only half a day, and you want to rent the other half to another customer. Chunking down your booking often helps, according to the nature of your business. Say, if you have a beach resort, most of your customers wouldn&#8217;t want to pay for the entire day, because they only spend the evening there.</p>\n<p>So, to cater for such customers, you can easily create a what we call &#8220;block&#8221;. What&#8217;s a block? A block is the minimum unit of your product which you are making available for booking.</p>\n<p>When you create a block for 3 hours with a buffer time of 30 minutes, you can sell it as many times you want. Setting a buffer time will allow you to give some time to your staff to refresh and redecorate the room for your next customer.</p>\n<h3>Making bookable products cost effective</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-003.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=can-now-book-products-events-hotels-anything-new-dokan-add&amp;x21811\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-80640\" src=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-003.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=can-now-book-products-events-hotels-anything-new-dokan-add&amp;x21811\" alt=\"new-booking-003\" width=\"914\" height=\"433\" srcset=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-003.png?x21811 914w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-003-300x142.png?x21811 300w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-003-768x364.png?x21811 768w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-003-600x284.png?x21811 600w?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=can-now-book-products-events-hotels-anything-new-dokan-add\" sizes=\"(max-width: 914px) 100vw, 914px\" /></a></p>\n<p>We understand that charging for bookable products can be difficult and people have so many different kind of booking requests that it get hard for you to charge and make profit. That is why, Dokan WC Booking allows you to set base costs, block costs and display costs all separately and chargeable and multipliable according to order.</p>\n<p>Say, if you set a base cost of 100$ for your booking, and you have a block of 2 hours, then you can charge the customers for each block separately and yet get payment for the initial booking.</p>\n<h3>Making bookings person and age limit specific</h3>\n<p>Sometimes your bookable products can have age sensitive or you might even have separate arrangements for different aged customers. For example, you have separate kid sized fun beds for children. So, if the customer can add that detail while he/she books for your suite, you will easily be able to arrange specifically for the members. You will also be able to give better service to your customers.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-004.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=can-now-book-products-events-hotels-anything-new-dokan-add&amp;x21811\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-80647\" src=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-004.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=can-now-book-products-events-hotels-anything-new-dokan-add&amp;x21811\" alt=\"new-booking-004\" width=\"923\" height=\"772\" srcset=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-004.png?x21811 923w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-004-300x251.png?x21811 300w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-004-768x642.png?x21811 768w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/new-booking-004-600x502.png?x21811 600w?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=can-now-book-products-events-hotels-anything-new-dokan-add\" sizes=\"(max-width: 923px) 100vw, 923px\" /></a></p>\n<h3>Add resources to your booking products</h3>\n<p>Say, you have pool attached to one of your suite, or you have a home theater which your customers can use for family entertainment. You can charge for that with your booking product as well. For this you need to add resources to your booking products.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/dokan-booking-vendor-dashboard.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=can-now-book-products-events-hotels-anything-new-dokan-add&amp;x21811\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-80642 size-full\" src=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/dokan-booking-vendor-dashboard-e1475561087310.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=can-now-book-products-events-hotels-anything-new-dokan-add&amp;x21811\" alt=\"dokan-booking-vendor-dashboard\" width=\"1126\" height=\"247\" srcset=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/dokan-booking-vendor-dashboard-e1475561087310.png?x21811 1126w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/dokan-booking-vendor-dashboard-e1475561087310-300x66.png?x21811 300w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/dokan-booking-vendor-dashboard-e1475561087310-768x168.png?x21811 768w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/dokan-booking-vendor-dashboard-e1475561087310-1024x225.png?x21811 1024w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/dokan-booking-vendor-dashboard-e1475561087310-600x132.png?x21811 600w?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=can-now-book-products-events-hotels-anything-new-dokan-add\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1126px) 100vw, 1126px\" /></a></p>\n<p>We have added a completely separate menu and listing for this kind of resources.</p>\n<p>Here is a video of how customers will purchase bookable products</p>\n<div style=\"width: 640px; \" class=\"wp-video\"><video class=\"wp-video-shortcode\" id=\"video-80622-2\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" preload=\"metadata\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"video/mp4\" src=\"http://docs.wedevs.com/assets/dokan-booking-customer-experience.mp4?_=2\" /><a href=\"http://docs.wedevs.com/assets/dokan-booking-customer-experience.mp4\">http://docs.wedevs.com/assets/dokan-booking-customer-experience.mp4</a></video></div>\n<h3>Documentation</h3>\n<p>We have created <a href=\"http://docs.wedevs.com/docs/dokan-add-ons/dokan-bookings/\" target=\"_blank\">a very elaborate document and video</a> for you so that it is easier for you to create.</p>\n\n<div style=\"display: block !important; margin:0 !important; padding: 0 !important\" id=\"wpsclp_locker_post_end_element\"></div><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/80622/can-now-book-products-events-hotels-anything-new-dokan-add/\">You can now book products, events and hotels, anything with this new Dokan add-on!</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:89:\"https://wedevs.com/80622/can-now-book-products-events-hotels-anything-new-dokan-add/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:30:\"com-wordpress:feed-additions:1\";a:1:{s:7:\"post-id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"80622\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"Upcoming New Features From Dokan Hack Month\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://wedevs.com/80438/upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://wedevs.com/80438/upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 27 Sep 2016 07:14:35 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Dokan\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"New Features\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"Plugins Release Notes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"dokan\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"latest update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"update\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://wedevs.com/?p=80438\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:598:\"<p>After successfully completing the Hack Month, a new version of Dokan is knocking at the door. It will bring a lot of new fixes and tweaks. In this article, we will talk about the new features that will make  Dokan Multivendor&#8230;\n<p class=\"read-more\"><a class=\"btn\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/80438/upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update/\">Read More &#8594;</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/80438/upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update/\">Upcoming New Features From Dokan Hack Month</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Mainul Kabir Aion\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16980:\"<p>After successfully completing the Hack Month, a new version of Dokan is knocking at the door. It will bring a lot of new fixes and tweaks. In this article, we will talk about the new features that will make <a href=\"https://wedevs.com/products/plugins/dokan/?utm_source=blog&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=post&amp;utm_content=aion&utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update\" target=\"_blank\"> Dokan Multivendor Marketplace</a> more awesome.</p>\n<h3>Crop store images</h3>\n<p>Now, you can crop your store banner image, profile picture, and gravatar to fit as you want. In the previous version, there was no option for cropping these images. Thus, the photos uploaded didn&#8217;t fit the screen. With this new feature, your banner and profile images will be best fitted to the screen. You will get this option on,</p>\n<p><strong>Seller Dashboard →settings→store settings.</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-crop-store-images.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-80483 size-full\" src=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-crop-store-images.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\" alt=\"dokan update - crop store images\" width=\"1130\" height=\"494\" srcset=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-crop-store-images.png?x21811 1130w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-crop-store-images-300x131.png?x21811 300w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-crop-store-images-768x336.png?x21811 768w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-crop-store-images-1024x448.png?x21811 1024w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-crop-store-images-600x262.png?x21811 600w?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1130px) 100vw, 1130px\" /></a></p>\n<h3>Option for selecting extra shipping cost recipient</h3>\n<p>In the admin area, a new option has been created for extra shipping fee. Now, you can choose who will get this additional fee  for shipping and tax. There are two recipients- admin and seller, in the list. You can select one from them.<br />\nThis option is available on <strong>WP Dashboard → Dokan → Settings → General</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-extra-shipping-cost-recepient.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-80482\" src=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-extra-shipping-cost-recepient.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\" alt=\"dokan extra shipping cost recepient\" width=\"1099\" height=\"497\" srcset=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-extra-shipping-cost-recepient.png?x21811 1099w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-extra-shipping-cost-recepient-300x136.png?x21811 300w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-extra-shipping-cost-recepient-768x347.png?x21811 768w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-extra-shipping-cost-recepient-1024x463.png?x21811 1024w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-extra-shipping-cost-recepient-600x271.png?x21811 600w?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1099px) 100vw, 1099px\" /></a></p>\n<h3>Dokan shortcode manager</h3>\n<p>Shortcodes are very handy when publishing a content within Dokan. But they are very difficult to remember. With the new version of Dokan, you don&#8217;t have to memorize the shortcodes. You can easily get them from post pages. You will see the Dokan logo on the toolbar. After clicking it, you will see all the shortcodes and use them when required.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Dokan-short-code-on-post.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-80481\" src=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Dokan-short-code-on-post.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\" alt=\"dokan short code on post\" width=\"1086\" height=\"469\" srcset=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Dokan-short-code-on-post.png?x21811 1086w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Dokan-short-code-on-post-300x130.png?x21811 300w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Dokan-short-code-on-post-768x332.png?x21811 768w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Dokan-short-code-on-post-1024x442.png?x21811 1024w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Dokan-short-code-on-post-600x259.png?x21811 600w?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1086px) 100vw, 1086px\" /></a></p>\n<h3><strong>Dokan m</strong>ulti-step<strong> settings wizard (For Admin)</strong></h3>\n<p>When you install Dokan plugin for the first time, you will get a step-by-step walkthrough settings just like WooCommerce. This will help you set up Dokan plugin and useful settings more easily.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-multi-step-wizard-for-admin.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-80480\" src=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-multi-step-wizard-for-admin.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\" alt=\"dokan multi-step wizard for admin\" width=\"918\" height=\"553\" srcset=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-multi-step-wizard-for-admin.png?x21811 918w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-multi-step-wizard-for-admin-300x181.png?x21811 300w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-multi-step-wizard-for-admin-768x463.png?x21811 768w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-multi-step-wizard-for-admin-600x361.png?x21811 600w?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update\" sizes=\"(max-width: 918px) 100vw, 918px\" /></a></p>\n<h3>Dokan multi-step settings wizard (For Seller)</h3>\n<p>Dokan sellers will get a similar walkthrough settings after registering as a seller. This will ease up the overall process for them and they will be able to set important options quite easily.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-multi-step-wizard-for-seller.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-80479\" src=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-multi-step-wizard-for-seller.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\" alt=\"dokan multi-step wizard for seller\" width=\"825\" height=\"527\" srcset=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-multi-step-wizard-for-seller.png?x21811 825w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-multi-step-wizard-for-seller-300x192.png?x21811 300w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-multi-step-wizard-for-seller-768x491.png?x21811 768w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-multi-step-wizard-for-seller-600x383.png?x21811 600w?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" /></a></p>\n<h3></h3>\n<h3>Advanced AJAX searching store list</h3>\n<p>Previously we had manual search for store listing. Now, the searching option has been enhanced with AJAX filtering. With this feature, you can search the store list by store name and username in real-time.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-store-list-ajax-search.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-80487\" src=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-store-list-ajax-search.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\" alt=\"dokan store list ajax search\" width=\"1157\" height=\"501\" srcset=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-store-list-ajax-search.png?x21811 1157w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-store-list-ajax-search-300x130.png?x21811 300w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-store-list-ajax-search-768x333.png?x21811 768w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-store-list-ajax-search-1024x443.png?x21811 1024w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-store-list-ajax-search-600x260.png?x21811 600w?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1157px) 100vw, 1157px\" /></a></p>\n<h3>Storewide discount</h3>\n<p>Using Dokan Plugin, you will get the ability to set storewide discount for your customers. You can set minimum order amount upon which customers will get the specific discount. Your customers must buy a minimum number of products within a single order to get this discount.</p>\n<p>To set this up navigate to <strong>Seller Dashboard → Settings → Store Settings</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-store-wide-discount.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-80478\" src=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-store-wide-discount.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\" alt=\"dokan store wide discount\" width=\"947\" height=\"407\" srcset=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-store-wide-discount.png?x21811 947w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-store-wide-discount-300x129.png?x21811 300w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-store-wide-discount-768x330.png?x21811 768w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-store-wide-discount-600x258.png?x21811 600w?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update\" sizes=\"(max-width: 947px) 100vw, 947px\" /></a></p>\n<h3>More products tab on single product page</h3>\n<p>You can set a new tab on your single product page stating more products. With it, customers will be able to view more products from your store. To set this up navigate to <strong>Seller Dashboard → Settings → Store Settings</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-more-product-tab.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-80486 size-full\" src=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-more-product-tab.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\" alt=\"dokan update - more product tab\" width=\"830\" height=\"445\" srcset=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-more-product-tab.png?x21811 830w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-more-product-tab-300x161.png?x21811 300w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-more-product-tab-768x412.png?x21811 768w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-more-product-tab-600x322.png?x21811 600w?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update\" sizes=\"(max-width: 830px) 100vw, 830px\" /></a></p>\n<h3></h3>\n<h3>Responsive front-end listing table</h3>\n<p>The front-end listing tables such as Order, Coupon and Product are responsive now. You will get the best user experience from these pages.</p>\n<h3>New report type for sellers</h3>\n<p>Using the new version of Dokan, sellers can generate new statements from the reports page. This is a transaction statement for seller showing relevant description for all the transactions made for a specific amount of time.</p>\n<p>To view this statement, navigate to <strong>Seller Dashboard → Reports → Statements</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-new-report-type.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-80477\" src=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-new-report-type.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\" alt=\"dokan new report type\" width=\"1065\" height=\"410\" srcset=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-new-report-type.png?x21811 1065w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-new-report-type-300x115.png?x21811 300w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-new-report-type-768x296.png?x21811 768w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-new-report-type-1024x394.png?x21811 1024w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-new-report-type-600x231.png?x21811 600w?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1065px) 100vw, 1065px\" /></a></p>\n<h3>New tracking and shipment status</h3>\n<p>With this feature, sellers will be able to add shipment tracking from the order page. Tracking number button at the bottom of the page will open a new window from where sellers can add three information- shipping provider, tracking number and shipping date.</p>\n<p>Customers will be able to view this information from their order board. They will also be able to track their products from there. You will find these option at <strong>Seller Dashboard → Order → Tracking Number</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-shipment-tracking-system.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-80485\" src=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-shipment-tracking-system.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update&amp;x21811\" alt=\"dokan shipment tracking system\" width=\"848\" height=\"530\" srcset=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-shipment-tracking-system.png?x21811 848w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-shipment-tracking-system-300x188.png?x21811 300w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-shipment-tracking-system-768x480.png?x21811 768w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-shipment-tracking-system-600x375.png?x21811 600w?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update\" sizes=\"(max-width: 848px) 100vw, 848px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Dokan multivendor marketplace is becoming bigger and better with every update. Check out your dashboard and read our newsletters to get more exciting news about Dokan.</p>\n\n<div style=\"display: block !important; margin:0 !important; padding: 0 !important\" id=\"wpsclp_locker_post_end_element\"></div><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/80438/upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update/\">Upcoming New Features From Dokan Hack Month</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://wedevs.com/80438/upcoming-new-features-in-dokan-update/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"17\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:30:\"com-wordpress:feed-additions:1\";a:1:{s:7:\"post-id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"80438\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"How to Use Product Review to Increase Popularity and Sales\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://wedevs.com/80353/use-product-review-popularity-sales/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://wedevs.com/80353/use-product-review-popularity-sales/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 19 Sep 2016 06:17:58 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Dokan\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Tips and Tricks\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"dokan\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"review\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://wedevs.com/?p=80353\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:632:\"<p>Did you know &#8211; about 63% customers tend to buy products online from stores which have more and better reviews and ratings? Reviews have proved to work like magic for your store&#8217;s sales and reputation. Product reviews are one of the most&#8230;\n<p class=\"read-more\"><a class=\"btn\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/80353/use-product-review-popularity-sales/\">Read More &#8594;</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/80353/use-product-review-popularity-sales/\">How to Use Product Review to Increase Popularity and Sales</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Mainul Kabir Aion\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8992:\"<p>Did you know &#8211; about 63% customers tend to buy products online from stores which have more and better reviews and ratings? Reviews have proved to work like magic for your store&#8217;s sales and reputation.</p>\n<p>Product reviews are one of the most efficient ways of branding and marketing of your online store. A good review can always increase the popularity and reliability of a product. You may know about the term &#8216;Word of Mouth&#8217;, which is a medium of communication between customers. Reviews serve the similar purpose for the online stores.</p>\n<p>When a customer reviews a product, they put their name behind the recommendation. This makes it even more valuable. Other customers often check the reviews and it influences their decision of buying.</p>\n<p>In today&#8217;s article, we shall talk about the benefits of product review in your Dokan store. You will also get to learn about useful tips on how you can increase your store popularity with it.</p>\n<p>Let&#8217;s have a look into the benefits before checking out the tips.</p>\n<h3>Authentic and free advertising for your store</h3>\n<p>With positive reviews and customer satisfaction, your store gets free advertising. Though it comes free, it is more effective than spending on advertisements or campaigns. Customers  expose your products and share their experience when they post a review. This hugely increases customer awareness, trust and reliability of your store.</p>\n<h3>Optimized search results to support your products</h3>\n<p>Search engines display results depending on the number of time a keyword is used. A customer posts a review mentioning your business name. Search engines like Google take that into account and display your business name in the search results more frequently.</p>\n<h3>Recommendations from customers can increase your sales</h3>\n<p>A product review is like peer recommendation and it is more trustworthy to your customers. Customers will look for other people who have already used that product online. When they find a review, they seem to believe it more than what is mentioned in the advertisements. Research shows that about 90% of customers trusted recommendations from people they know and 70% trusted reviews posted online. This makes reviews a powerful form of marketing.</p>\n<h3>Constructive suggestions open new doors of improvement</h3>\n<p>You will get suggestions from your customers through reviews. This can be a great thing as you will get to improve your products by resolving customer problems. This can turn out to be a great business practice and increase customer loyalty. Product reviews also provide you criticism, which leads to new opportunity and improvement.</p>\n<h3>Attracts more customers and connects them</h3>\n<p>Product reviews are a form of communication which creates a better understanding. It also showcases your products online. By this way, other customers can see them and develops a relationship between customers.</p>\n<h3>Tips to use product review for increased popularity</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>You can ask your customers personally to post a review after purchase.</li>\n<li>The review process in Dokan stores is very simple, customers can easily post reviews.</li>\n<li>You can also offer loyalty points for each review to your customers.</li>\n<li>Optimize your store for better reviews.</li>\n<li>Approve both positive and negative reviews as a mixture will make things more believable.</li>\n<li>Consider customer suggestions for improvement.</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>Product reviews work amazingly in Dokan</h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://wedevs.com/products/plugins/dokan/?utm_source=blog&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=post&amp;utm_content=aion&utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=use-product-review-popularity-sales\">Dokan Multivendor</a> has built in product review feature, which can a great tool to increase your product popularity. Navigate to- <strong>Seller Dashboard → Reviews</strong>. You will find all the reviews segmented as published, pending, spam and also trash. You can approve pending reviews and display them on your store page.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-product-review.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=use-product-review-popularity-sales&amp;x21811\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-80361\" src=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-product-review.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=use-product-review-popularity-sales&amp;x21811\" alt=\"dokan-product-review\" width=\"1128\" height=\"456\" srcset=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-product-review.png?x21811 1128w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-product-review-300x121.png?x21811 300w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-product-review-768x310.png?x21811 768w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-product-review-1024x414.png?x21811 1024w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-product-review-600x243.png?x21811 600w?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=use-product-review-popularity-sales\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1128px) 100vw, 1128px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Click on the Pending tab and you will see all the pending reviews and you can approve the ones  you want. All you have to do is to check the review and select the action you want and click Submit button.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-product-review-approval.jpg?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=use-product-review-popularity-sales&amp;x21811\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-80362\" src=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-product-review-approval.jpg?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=use-product-review-popularity-sales&amp;x21811\" alt=\"dokan-product-review-approval\" width=\"1161\" height=\"609\" srcset=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-product-review-approval.jpg?x21811 1161w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-product-review-approval-300x157.jpg?x21811 300w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-product-review-approval-768x403.jpg?x21811 768w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-product-review-approval-1024x537.jpg?x21811 1024w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-product-review-approval-600x315.jpg?x21811 600w?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=use-product-review-popularity-sales\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1161px) 100vw, 1161px\" /></a></p>\n<p>This will display the approved reviews on the product page and also your store page. You can display reviews as peer recommendations on your store page and it effectively increases the popularity of your store.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-seller-store-review.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=use-product-review-popularity-sales&amp;x21811\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-80365 size-full\" src=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-seller-store-review.png?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=use-product-review-popularity-sales&amp;x21811\" alt=\"use product review for more popularity\" width=\"1177\" height=\"931\" srcset=\"https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-seller-store-review.png?x21811 1177w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-seller-store-review-300x237.png?x21811 300w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-seller-store-review-768x607.png?x21811 768w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-seller-store-review-1024x810.png?x21811 1024w, https://wedevs-com-wedevs.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/dokan-seller-store-review-600x475.png?x21811 600w?utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=use-product-review-popularity-sales\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1177px) 100vw, 1177px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Did you like how Dokan handles reviews? You can <a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-success\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/products/plugins/dokan/?utm_source=blog&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=post&amp;utm_content=aion&utm_source=wedevs.com&medium=blog&utm_campaign=use-product-review-popularity-sales\">get Dokan for yourself!</a></p>\n\n<div style=\"display: block !important; margin:0 !important; padding: 0 !important\" id=\"wpsclp_locker_post_end_element\"></div><p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com/80353/use-product-review-popularity-sales/\">How to Use Product Review to Increase Popularity and Sales</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wedevs.com\">weDevs</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://wedevs.com/80353/use-product-review-popularity-sales/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{